	        <h2 id="what-you-get">What this gives you</h2>
	        <ul>
	          <li><span class="check">1</span><span>A Cowork Project that knows your profile, goals, agenda, people, and assistant rules.</span></li>
	          <li><span class="check">2</span><span>A live <strong>Daily Brief</strong> page: your schedule, goals, meeting prep, to-dos, and email drafts, refreshed every morning.</span></li>
	          <li><span class="check">3</span><span>One validated assistant plugin with the reusable skills bundled together, including <code>setup</code> that wires it all up for you.</span></li>
	          <li><span class="check">4</span><span>A weekday morning routine that preps your meetings, drafts your replies, and updates your brief on its own.</span></li>
	          <li><span class="check">5</span><span>Two ways to use it: Cowork on your computer and Dispatch on your phone.</span></li>
	        </ul>
